        <mxCell id="pq0AM1h1IiiyBDEnBlEK-41" value="TODOs:&lt;div&gt;- all models should have a config JSON file (yaml or w/e later...)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- config file should include model hyperparameters AND training parameters&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;train.py&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- takes any model class and config&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- default is uses all training and validation samples but does random sampling if the config&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- unit_train.py no longer needed if the config file now specifies one epoch&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacingLeft=6;spacingRight=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
